This End-to-End BI solution transforms massive, unstructured social media data into strategic insights for the Algerian telecommunications market (Djezzy, Mobilis, Ooredoo).


Architecture & Engineering
Data Acquisition: Asynchronous scraping using protocol interception of the Facebook GraphQL API.


NLP Engine: Dialectal sentiment analysis (Arabizi/Darija) using XLM-RoBERTa.


Industrial Automation: 100% autonomous refresh cycle managed by Power Automate Desktop.


Business Intelligence Highlights
The project utilizes a Star Schema optimized for high-performance DAX queries.

Strategic KPIs (DAX)

Net Sentiment Score (NSS): Measures net customer satisfaction.

Share of Voice (SOV %): Relative brand visibility against competitors.

Polarity Index: Ratio of positive vs. negative brand engagement.


Shutterstock
Automation Workflow (RPA)
To ensure data freshness without manual intervention, a RPA flow orchestrates the pipeline:

Integrity Check: Active monitoring of 6 CSV sources.


UI Automation: Automated UI interaction with Power BI Desktop to trigger data refresh.
